Chief Constables ' Message really welcome interest joining Police Force . privilege lead teams Surrey Police Sussex Police continuously work selflessly tirelessly order keep people counties safe . looking talented inspirational people put needs public heart everything want make difference . feel person want hear . wish best application . Skills & Experience Successful candidates expected outstanding problem solving skills , experience querying databases using SQL working knowledge latest business intelligence tool PowerBI ( including DAX ) . preferred candidates also familiar analysing data information , making inferences explaining statistical concepts ability manage requirements prioritise tasks across diverse range subject areas . importantly must exceptional communicator ; expected maintain good working relationships within organisation , ( including key stakeholders internal customers ) external agencies Home Office HMICFRS . also expected present findings analysis senior leaders , use insight analysis support decision making . Work Us ? Policing exciting 24/7 business commitments outside work . ’ invested supporting people balance life work encourage flexible working . take pride looking people offer variety benefits ; • career progression • contributory pension scheme ( LGPS ) • generous annual leave allowance • discounts everyday spend • on-site gyms range sports clubs • generous supportive parental leave • financial mental wellbeing guidance support • discounted contributory healthcare scheme Please use following links information benefits working Surrey Police Sussex Police . Information information please contact Switch Whitcher-Horn ( ) Previously unsuccessful candidates applied post past 6 months reapply . Development deployment new APIs within defined timelines . Zero critical defects production post-deployment . Positive feedback stakeholders users regarding upgraded APIs . Mule Anypoint Studio - Primary development environment designing debugging Mule ESB flows . RabbitMQ - messaging bus facilitates communication different services/components system reliably queuing , routing , delivering messages . Java - Core language backend services , necessary writing , maintaining , troubleshooting applications integrate Mule ESB . MySQL Database - Database management querying , essential accessing , updating , managing application data . Bamboo CI/CD - Continuous integration deployment tool automating builds , testing , deployments dev production environments . Stash ( Git ) - Version control managing tracking code changes , supporting collaboration across development team . Jira - Issue project tracking tool , used coordinate production support requests , development tasks , release management . Qualifications : Bachelor ’ degree Computer Science , Engineering , related field , equivalent experience . 3+ years Mule : confident understanding MuleSoft ’ Anypoint Platform , including API development , integration patterns Mule 4 architecture . Upgrading knowledge : Experience upgrading Mule x Mule 4.4 including migration code , connectors , dependencies Connector Upgrades : Familiarity updating legacy connectors Mule 4 compatible versions building bespoke migrating new connectors . Proficiency backend programming languages Java , Python , Node.js , similar . Familiarity production environments CI/CD pipelines . Experience service monitoring , debugging , troubleshooting tools . Ability work collaboratively fast-paced environment , balancing multiple priorities . Mule Anypoint Studio - Primary development environment designing debugging Mule ESB flows . RabbitMQ - messaging bus facilitates communication different services/components system reliably queuing , routing , delivering messages . Java - Core language backend services , necessary writing , maintaining , troubleshooting applications integrate Mule ESB . MySQL Database - Database management querying , essential accessing , updating , managing application data . Bamboo CI/CD - Continuous integration deployment tool automating builds , testing , deployments dev production environments . Stash ( Git ) - Version control managing tracking code changes , supporting collaboration across development team . Jira - Issue project tracking tool , used coordinate production support requests , development tasks , release management . Upgrading knowledge : Experience upgrading Mule x Mule 4.4 including migration code , connectors , dependencies Connector Upgrades : Familiarity updating legacy connectors Mule 4 compatible versions building bespoke migrating new connectors . Proficiency backend programming languages Java , Python , Node.js , similar . Familiarity production environments CI/CD pipelines . Experience service monitoring , debugging , troubleshooting tools . Ability work collaboratively fast-paced environment , balancing multiple priorities . subject : recommendation : Mule Developer
body : Hello Divyaprakash , recommend job . Take look see want apply . Mule Developer H Revenue & Customs ( HMRC ) Stratford , East London ( E15 ) Contract 1 day ago Apply https : //click.cwjobs.co.uk/f/a/jU2on7jkmEyJ-t02qD6s6w~~/AAAmIgA~/RgRpd4x6P4RHAWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LmN3am9icy5jby51ay9Kb2JTZWFyY2gvRW1haWxMaW5rLmFzcHg_~ Role : seeking skilled Mule Developer join Check Challenge Appeal ( CCA ) development team . dedicated , friendly team made product roles technical developers/testers – delivering Agile manner passionate interested customers behalf Value Office Agency ( VOA ) . ideal future colleague part Team Developers/Testers responsible upgrade Mule 4.4 Responsibilities : Mule developer responsible following tasks : Upgrade APIs : Rebuild existing Mule 3.x APIs Mule 4.4 adhering updated best practice specifications . Development New APIs : Build required APIs Mule 4.4 best practice specifications directed . Testing Validation : Collaborate testers ensure APIs meet functional , non-functional , performance criteria . Debug , resolve issues , conduct regression testing necessary . Collaboration Team : Work closely within wider team CCA developers testers ensure consistency quality deliverables . Documentation : Document processes , updates , lessons learned provide reference future upgrades . Deliverables : Upgraded/enhanced CCA APIs compatible Mule 4.4 . Comprehensive testing results documentation . Deployment-ready APIs ensuring smooth production transition . Technical documentation APIs rebuilt/enhanced work . Ongoing/Continuous Improvement : Identify opportunities process code improvements within production environment . Proactively engage troubleshooting , optimising , scaling backend services support growing business needs . Performance Metrics : Successful migration identified Mule 3.x APIs 4.4 . Development deployment new APIs within defined timelines . Zero critical defects production post-deployment . Positive feedback stakeholders users regarding upgraded APIs . Technologies : Mule ESB ( Enterprise Service Bus ) - Key integration platform managing orchestrating service connectivity data flows applications . Mule Anypoint Studio - Primary development environment designing debugging Mule ESB flows . RabbitMQ - messaging bus facilitates communication different services/components system reliably queuing , routing , delivering messages . Java - Core language backend services , necessary writing , maintaining , troubleshooting applications integrate Mule ESB . MySQL Database - Database management querying , essential accessing , updating , managing application data . Elastic Stack ( Elasticsearch , Kibana ) - Primarily used monitoring log analysis ; leveraging stack diagnose production issues , track service performance , support troubleshooting . Bamboo CI/CD - Continuous integration deployment tool automating builds , testing , deployments dev production environments . Stash ( Git ) - Version control managing tracking code changes , supporting collaboration across development team . Jira - Issue project tracking tool , used coordinate production support requests , development tasks , release management . Qualifications : Bachelor ’ degree Computer Science , Engineering , related field , equivalent experience . 3+ years Mule : confident understanding MuleSoft ’ Anypoint Platform , including API development , integration patterns Mule 4 architecture . Upgrading knowledge : Experience upgrading Mule x Mule 4.4 including migration code , connectors , dependencies Connector Upgrades : Familiarity updating legacy connectors Mule 4 compatible versions building bespoke migrating new connectors . Proficiency backend programming languages Java , Python , Node.js , similar . Familiarity production environments CI/CD pipelines . Experience service monitoring , debugging , troubleshooting tools . Ability work collaboratively fast-paced environment , balancing multiple priorities .
